text: Malokazakkulovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Amangildinsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 309 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 60 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Malokazakkulovo
